"Eligible institution" means:
Each public senior higher education institution identified in § 10-101(m) or § 12-101(b)(5) of this article or its affiliated foundation; and
The following community college campuses or their affiliated foundations:
Allegany;
Anne Arundel;
Baltimore City;
Calvert;
Carroll;
Catonsville;
Cecil;
Charles;
Chesapeake;
Dundalk;
Essex;
Frederick;
Garrett;
Germantown;
Hagerstown;
Harford;
Howard;
Prince George's;
Rockville;
St. Mary's;
Takoma Park; and
Wor-Wic.
